**Interview Summary**

Don Johnson | Trane Technologies

CEM, Sr. Account Manager - Pacific Southwest, Commercial HVAC Americas

Conducted by Clayton Hester & Victor Pan | March 2026

| **Why This Interview Matters** Don Johnson is a rare find: a Certified Energy Manager who has worked on both sides of the meter. He spent 9 years at El Paso Electric as the commercial key account rep for their largest customers, overseeing energy efficiency programs. He has also spent nearly 20 years on the solutions side at Carrier, Johnson Controls, and now Trane. His perspective bridges the gap between how utilities bill, how customers (mis)understand their bills, and how energy solutions providers sell into that confusion. This interview produced actionable intelligence on product features, competitive positioning, and go-to-market strategy. |
